name: George McINTOSH v. Antonio A. MOREY

parties: George McINTOSH v. Antonio A. MOREY.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The defendant’s motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is assigned to the motion calendar for oral argument.

attorneys: John Quattrocchi, Jr., Providence, for plaintiff.
Hanson, Curran & Parks, Robert D. Par-rillo, Providence, for defendant.

Hanson, Curran & Parks, Robert D. Par-rillo, Providence, for defendant.
